    {
      "sender_name": "Jaideep Raha",
      "timestamp_ms": 1628568189636,
      "content": "*A beautiful poem by Lee Tzu Pheng (Singapore Cultural Medallion winner)*\n\nSip your Tea\nNice and Slow, \n\nNo one Ever knows \nwhen it\u00e2\u0080\u0099s Time to Go,\nThere\u00e2\u0080\u0099ll be no Time \nto enjoy the Glow,\nSo sip your Tea\nNice and Slow... \u00f0\u009f\u0091\u008c\u00f0\u009f\u008f\u00bb\n\nLife is too Short but \nfeels pretty Long,\nThere\u00e2\u0080\u0099s too Much to do , \nso much going Wrong, \nAnd Most of the Time You Struggle to be Strong,\nBefore it\u00e2\u0080\u0099s too Late \nand it\u00e2\u0080\u0099s time to Go,\nSip your Tea\nNice and Slow... \u00f0\u009f\u0091\u008c\u00f0\u009f\u008f\u00bb\n\nSome Friends stay, \nothers Go away,\nLoved ones are Cherished, \nbut not all will Stay ,\nKids will Grow up \nand Fly away,\nThere\u00e2\u0080\u0099s really no Saying how Things will Go,\nSo sip your Tea\nNice and Slow... \u00e2\u0098\u0095\n\nIn the End it\u00e2\u0080\u0099s really \nall about Understanding Love,\nFor this World  \nand in the Stars above,\nAppreciate and Value who truly Cares, \nSmile and Breathe \nand let your Worries go,\nSo, Just Sip your Tea\nNice and Slow.... \u00e2\u0098\u0095\n*This poem is beyond all relationships*\n\nWe are nothing without each other in life... \nStay Connected\u00f0\u009f\u0099\u008f",
